<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Site Name: Remote Work Resources and Tools</h1>
        <p>Reason for selection: With the rise of remote work trends, there is a growing demand for centralized resources and tools to support individuals and businesses in optimizing their remote work experience. This project aligns well with my interests and allows me to contribute to a meaningful and practical resource for remote workers worldwide.</p>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <h2>Site Purpose</h2>
            <p>The site will serve as a comprehensive platform offering resources, guides, and tools for individuals and businesses transitioning to or currently engaged in remote work. It will feature curated articles, productivity tools, remote job listings, community forums, events/webinars, resource libraries, interactive tools, expert interviews/podcasts, and more. The content will cover topics such as setting up a home office, managing remote teams, effective communication strategies, remote job opportunities, and productivity enhancement.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Scenarios</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>What are the best tools for managing remote teams?</li>
                <li>Where can I find remote job listings?</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Color Schema</h2>
            <p>Primary Color: <span class="color-box" style="background-color: #4CAF50;">#4CAF50</span> (used for headings)</p>
            <p>Secondary Color: <span class="color-box" style="background-color: #333;">#333</span> (used for accents)</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Typography</h2>
            <p>Main Font: Arial (used for body text)</p>
            <p>Heading Font: Helvetica (used for headings)</p>
        </section>
